<plot>The docudrama Opus Dei Unveiled is a fascinating inside look at Opus Dei - considered by some to be the most controversial organization in the Catholic Church. From its humble birth in Spain in 1928 to its remarkable global imprint and influence throughout the Catholic Church, discover the real story behind the spiritually-demanding and controversial lifestyle of Opus Dei's 87,000 worldwide members.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?414950</url></doc>
